// @check
// @error for-range step must be i32
// A `for … step` literal past the i32 range is REJECTED — never silently
// truncated into a different step (4294967297 wraps to 1 as a 32-bit value).
// The checker rejects it up front; the emitter's constant fold carries its own
// `numLexFitsI32` backstop so the truncation cannot re-enter through any
